Package: ncontRanalyser
Type: Package
Title: 'CCP4 NCONT Antibody-Antigen Data Tranformation and Analysis'
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-07-14
Authors@R: person("Sara", "Procacci", , "saraprocacci04@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Transforms data from CCP4 NCONT (v8.0.019) to dataframe format and 
    calculates n/d (count/ distance) ratios in antibody-antigen interactions. 
    Use a reference structure to calculate n/d quartiles (or manually input these) 
    and applies these to structures with mutated antigen. 
